<details>
	<summary>Q - Where is Toki Pona spoken?</summary>
	<p>
		A - Toki Pona is spoken all over the world, but the highest concentration of
		Toki Pona speakers is in Europe and North America. Most Toki Pona speakers
		use it online, but a few also choose to attend IRL meetups!
	</p>
	<a href='https://ma.pona.la/'
		><img
			src='/sitelen/lipu-pi-ma-ale.png'
			alt='A world map with hundreds of pins'
		/></a
	>
</details>

<details>
	<summary>Meet in person!</summary>

	<Card url='https://ma.pona.la/' img='/sitelen/ma-ale/lipu-ma.png'
		>Find local Toki Pona <b>speakers near you</b> on a <abbr
			title="'document of land'">lipu ma</abbr
		>!</Card
	>
	<ul>
		<li>
			<a href='https://discord.gg/U7XfbFcFfb'>tenpo kulupu pi ma Elopa</a>,
			yearly meetup in Europe.<br />Berlin 2024, Strasbourg 2025, <a href='https://mallonge.net/maelopa2026'>Tiana 2026</a>
		</li><li>
			<a href='https://discord.gg/kTU7Bsa2TR'>tenpo kulupu pi ma Amelika lete</a
			>, yearly meetup in North America.<br />Chicago 2024, Seattle 2025, <a href='https://kulupu.la/en/nujo2026/'>New
			York 2026</a
			>
		</li>
	</ul>
</details>

<h2>Literature</h2>
<ul>
	<li>
		<a href='https://liputenpo.org'>lipu tenpo</a>: Toki Pona magazine.
		Educational, prose, poems, and other fun stuff!
	</li>
	<li>
		<a href='https://utala.pona.la'>utala musi</a>: yearly contest of Toki Pona
		literature. Read poems and longer original works!
	</li>
	<li>
		<a href='https://lipu.pona.la'>Library</a> collecting all creative texts
	</li>
</ul>

